{
  "stem": "26672.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. you always considered different people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ah, I remember things, when my mother used to cook, especially for-- for people, poor people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, as children, used to take canned food down to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'd be going to one woman, who was living in an attic, and we were taking-- we were walking up on, partly, a ladder to reach her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taking food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a great joy for us, children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Seems to be complete blockage of the dates and names in the-- I remember things but never the dates or anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we get together, surprising enough, when we get together with other boys, we always talking.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Things come to-- to mind, you know, of what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean recently, my friend, Monty Tabachnik, reminded me that, when we went back from-- after liberation-- I'm going on with it-- after liberation, at Theresienstadt, him and I went back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somehow we felt that maybe we still had some family-- mine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he told them the way-- this is a story on its own, how we went to Poland and no papers and how we went back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we met up with my aunt, who survived, and his two sisters, who survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They eventually went to Canada, one who's still alive and one who died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My aunt is not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She went-- eventually went to Israel, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we went-- on the way, we met people and told us, don't go into your home towns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The pogroms, the Poles are still killing Jews, those, the few that survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I felt, now!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Me, I'm a big man now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm not frightened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This Monty Tabachnik went on to Lodz, because he was told his sisters were in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
